Moody's Investors Service Inc said itmay upgrade the ratings on 1.45 billion dlrs of debt of SCIHoldings Inc.    The agency cited SCI's announcement that it agreed to sellfor 1.3 billion dlrs six television stations and relatedproperties to a joint venture formed by SCI and GillettHoldings Inc. While financing details are not available, theagency said SCI's debt should decline as a result of the sale.    BCI currently carries Ba-3 zero coupon senior notes and B-2senior subordinated debentures. The BCI unit StorerCommunications Inc has B-2 subordinated debentures. Reuter&#3;